<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oleo+Script:wght@400;700&family=Pacifico&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://api.dsapsol.com/favicon.jpg" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>Educational Activities</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'poppins';
        }

        :root {
            --prime: <%=direction %>
        }

        .about-most-outsider {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: auto;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 20px;
            flex-direction: var(--prime);
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
            padding-right: 40px;
        }

        .about-text h2 {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-text h1 {
            color: #343a40;
            font-size: 48px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-text h1 span {
            color: #0cc0df;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .about-text p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .about-text p strong {
            color: #343a40;
            font-weight: bold;
            /* background-color: #e0f7e9; */
            padding: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .about-text .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #f36f45;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .about-text .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: #357ab8;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 425px;
            max-height: 400px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .about-text {
                padding-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .about-image {
                margin-top: 20px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .about-text h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .about-text p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .about-text .cta-btn {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }

        .unique-img-section {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            /* Pure white background */
            text-align: center;
            /* Centering the images */
        }

        /* Styling for the custom row container */
        .custom-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            /* Adds spacing between columns */
        }

        /* Styling for each column */
        .custom-col {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 23%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        /* Styling for the images */
        .image-item {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            /* Fixed height for the images */
            object-fit: cover;
            /* Ensures images cover the area without stretching */
            border-radius: 12px;
            /* Rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            /* Subtle shadow for depth */
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            /* Smooth transition for hover */
        }
        
        /* Hover effect on images */
        .image-item:hover {
            border: 1px solid #0cc0df;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            /* Slight zoom effect */
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            /* Stronger shadow on hover */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .custom-col {
                max-width: none;
            }

            .custom-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../../common/header') %>
        <div class="about-most-outsider">
            <div class="about-container">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h1><span>EDUCATIONAL ACTIVITIES</span></h1>
                    <p>The International University of Kyrgyzstan (IUK) is renowned for its <strong>holistic
                            approach</strong>
                        to medical
                        education, emphasizing both <strong>theoretical knowledge</strong> and <strong>clinical
                            expertise</strong>. The curriculum integrates
                        <strong>medical science fundamentals</strong>, hands-on <strong>clinical experience</strong>,
                        and a
                        commitment to compassionate <strong>patient care</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p>IUK students participate in a range of activities designed to build strong <strong>medical
                            competencies</strong>. Lectures
                        and seminars provide foundational knowledge, while laboratory sessions and <strong>clinical
                            rotations</strong> offer
                        practical exposure to the latest <strong>medical technologies</strong> and practices.
                        Partnerships
                        with
                        leading <strong>hospitals</strong>
                        and healthcare institutions ensure students gain <strong>real-world experience</strong> in
                        patient
                        care
                        and medical
                        research.</p>
                    <p>The faculties at IUK are experienced <strong>medical professionals</strong>, conducting
                        workshops,
                        simulations, and case
                        studies to enhance critical thinking, <strong>diagnostic skills</strong>, and teamwork. These
                        activities
                        prepare students
                        to adapt to the evolving <strong>healthcare landscape</strong> and address complex medical
                        challenges.
                    </p>
                    <p>Beyond academics, IUK hosts <strong>medical conferences</strong>, guest lectures from prominent
                        healthcare experts, and
                        interdisciplinary projects, fostering <strong>research</strong>, <strong>innovation</strong>,
                        and
                        exploration of new fields in medical
                        science. The university’s focus on <strong>medical research</strong> and <strong>social
                            responsibility</strong> encourages students to
                        contribute to advancements in healthcare.</p>
                    <p>The IUK library offers over 128,000 electronic scientific publications, with a collection of
                        18,000
                        printed books, including <strong>textbooks</strong>, reference books,
                        <strong>encyclopedias</strong>,
                        dissertation abstracts, periodicals,
                        dictionaries, and manuals, supporting students’ academic and research needs.
                    </p>
                    <a class="cta-btn" href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/edumain.png" alt="Image 1" />
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/edumain2.png" alt="Image 1" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="unique-img-section">
            <div class="custom-row">
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/edu1.png" alt="Image 1" class="image-item">
                </div>
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/edu2.png" alt="Image 2" class="image-item">
                </div>
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/edu3.JPG" alt="Image 3" class="image-item">
                </div>
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/edu4.JPG" alt="Image 4" class="image-item">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <%- include('../../common/footer') %>
</body>

</html>